<plot>Alex is a 13-year-old newcomer from Russia, and hated by the local kids. One night, he has a chance of getting accepted by pulling a cruel trick on an old woman neighbor. Alex passes the "test" and gets accepted, but faces the consequences of his deed, and realizes that being part of the "group" is not everything in life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?029252</url></doc>
